  "prompt": "What's your definition of \"friends\"?",
  "response": "Friends are individuals who share a bond of mutual affection, trust, and support. They enjoy each other's company, engage in common interests, and provide emotional, and sometimes physical, assistance when needed. Friendships can vary in intensity and can be based on different factors such as shared experiences, values, or circumstances. Overall, friends are people who enrich our lives and contribute positively to our well-being.",
